tp://www.vpap.org/elections/chamber/4 Virginia Public Access Project: House of Delegates]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20091105061020/https://www.voterinfo.sbe.virginia.gov/election/DATA/2009/37C2EDEB-FACB-44C1-AF70-05FB616DCD62/UnOfficial/8_s.shtml Virginia State Board of Elections]\n*[http://hamptonroads.com/2009/11/villanueva-declared-winner-21st-district-race Villanueva declared winner in 21st District race]\n\n[[Category:2009 Virginia elections|*]]\n[[Category:Virginia General Assembly elections]]\n[[Category:2001 state legislature elections in the United States|Virginia]]\n", "text_old": "{{Citations missing|date=August 2009}}\n{{Infobox election\n| election_name = 2009 Virginia House of Delegates election\n| country = Virginia\n| type = legislative\n| ongoing = no\n| previous_election = 2007 Virginia House of Delegates election\n| previous_year = 2007\n| election_date = November 3, 2009\n| next_election = 2011 Virginia House of Delegates election\n| next_year = 2011\n| seats_for_election = All 100 seats in the [[Virginia House of Delegates]]\n| majority_seats = 51\n| turnout = 40.4%<ref>{{cite web|title=Registration/Turnout Statistics|url=https://www.elections.virginia.gov/resultsreports/registration-statistics/registrationturnout-statistics/index.html|publisher=Virginia Department of Elections|accessdate=January 24, 2018}}</ref> {{increase}}\n| image1 = [[File:Bill Howell, Speaker of the Virginia House of Delegates (Republican).png|160x160px]]\n| leader1 = [[William J. Howell|Bill Howell]]\n| leader_since1 = January 8, 2003\n| party1 = Republican Party (United States)\n| leaders_seat1 = [[Virginia's 28th House of Delegates district|28th]]\n| last_election1 = '''53'''\n| seats1 = '''59'''\n| seat_change1 = {{increase}} 6\n| popular_vote1 = '''1,047,069'''\n| percentage1 = '''56.8%'''\n| swing1 = {{increase}} 5.8%\n| title = [[List of Speakers of the Virginia House of Delegates|Speaker]]\n| before_election = [[William J. Howell|Bill Howell]]\n| before_party 