entina)|Copa de Oro]]\n|date= January 27, 2016\n|time= 22:10\n|team1=[[Boca Juniors]]\n|score= 0\u20132\n|report= [http://www.afa.org.ar/deposito/html/v3/index.html?channel=deportes.futbol.copadeoro.257723&lang=es_LA Report]\n|team2=[[Estudiantes de La Plata|Estudiantes (LP)]]\n|goals1= [[Pablo P\u00e9rez|P\u00e9rez]] {{yel|16}}<br />[[Andr\u00e9s Ch\u00e1vez|Ch\u00e1vez]] {{yel|53}}\n|goals2= [[Gast\u00f3n Fern\u00e1ndez|Fern\u00e1ndez]] {{goal|35}}<br /> [[El\u00edas Umeres|Umeres]] {{goal|47}}<br /> [[Santiago Ascacibar|Ascacibar]] {{yel|62}}<br />[[Carlos Auzqui|Auzqui]] {{yel|78}}<br />[[Juli\u00e1n Marchioni|Marchioni]] {{yel|88}}\n|location  = [[Mar del Plata]]\n|stadium= [[Estadio Jos\u00e9 Mar\u00eda Minella]]\n|attendance=\n|referee= [[Pedro Arga\u00f1araz]]\n|result= L\n}}\n\n{{football box collapsible\n|round=[[Torneos de Verano (Argentina)|Copa Luis B. Nofal]]\n|date= January 30, 2016\n|time= 22:10\n|team1=[[Boca Juniors]]\n|score= 0\u20131\n|aggregatescore=0\u20132\n|report= [http://www.afa.org.ar/deposito/html/v3/index.html?channel=deportes.futbol.coparevancha.258164&lang=es_LA Report]\n|team2=[[Club Atl\u00e9tico River Plate|River Plate]]\n|goals1= [[Carlos Tevez|Tevez]] {{yel|57}}<br />[[Nicol\u00e1s Lodeiro|Lodeiro]] {{yel|64}}\n|goals2= [[\u00c9der \u00c1lvarez Balanta|\u00c1lvarez Balanta]] {{yel|23}}<br />[[Gabriel Mercado|Mercado]] {{yel|52}}<br />[[Rodrigo Mora|Mora]] {{goal|80|pen.}} {{yel|81}}<br />[[Leonel Vangioni|Vangioni]] {{yel|90}}\n|location  = [[Mendoza, Argentina|Mendoza]]\n|stadium= [[Estadio Malvinas Argentinas]]\n|attendance=\n|referee= [[N\u00e9stor Pitana]]\n|result= L\n}}\n\n==Competitions==\n\n===Overall===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!scope=col|Competition\n!scope=col|Started round\n!scope=col|Final position/round\n!scope=col|First match\n!scope=col|Last match\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[2016 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|Primera Divisi\u00f3n]]\n| \u2013 