 G. McWatters (I) 11.3%\n|-{{party shading/Democratic}}\n| [[Virginia's 35th House of Delegates district|35th]]\n| bgcolor = \"lightgrey\" |[[Jeannemarie Devolites-Davis|Jeannemarie Devolites]]\n| Republican\n| 1997\n| Elected to State Senate\n| '''Steve Shannon (D) 51.9%'''<BR> Robert M McDowell  (R) 48.1%\n|-\n| [[Virginia's 37th House of Delegates district|37th]]\n| [[Chap Petersen]]\n| Democratic\n| 2001\n| Reelected\n| '''[[Chap Petersen]] (D) 59.5%''' <BR> [[Jack Rust]] (R) 40.5%\n|-\n| [[Virginia's 41st House of Delegates district|41st]]\n| [[Jim Dillard]]\n| Republican\n| 1980\n| Reelected\n| '''[[Jim Dillard]] (R) 63.5%''' <BR> Michael J. Golden (I) 26.9% <BR> John M. Wolfe (I) 9.2% \n|-{{party shading/Democratic}}\n| [[Virginia's 43rd House of Delegates district|43rd]]\n| bgcolor = \"lightgrey\" |[[Tom Bolvin]]\n| Republican\n| 1997\n| Defeated\n| '''[[Mark D. Sickles]] (D) 53.8%''' <BR> [[Tom Bolvin]] (R) 46.1%\n|-\n| [[Virginia's 44th House of Delegates district|44th]]\n| [[Kristen J. Amundson]]\n| Democrat\n| 1999\n| Reelected\n| '''[[Kristen J. Amundson]] (D) 56.3%''' <BR> David Kennedy (R) 43.6% \n|-\n| [[Virginia's 45th House of Delegates district|45th]]\n| [[Marian Van Landingham]]\n| Democratic\n| 1981\n| Reelected\n| '''[[Marian Van Landingham]] (D) 63.6%''' <BR> Robert J. Test (R) 36.2%\n|-\n| [[Virginia's 47th House of Delegates district|47th]]\n| bgcolor = \"lightgrey\" |[[Jim Almand]]\n| Democratic\n| 1981\n| Retired\n| '''[[Al Eisenberg]] (D) 65.5%''' <BR> R. Christian Hoff (R) 34.4%\n|-\n| [[Virginia's 48th House of Delegates district|48th]]\n| [[Robert H. Brink]]\n| Democratic\n| 1997\n| Reelected\n| ''' [[Robert H. Brink]] (D) 60.9%''' <BR> Steve Sass (R) 39.0%\n|-\n| [[Virginia's 52nd House of Delegates district|52nd]]\n| bgcolor = \"lightgrey\" |[[Jack Rollison]]\n| Republican\n| 2003\n| Defeated in Primary\n| '''[[Jeff Frederick]] (R) 56.7%''' <BR> Charles Taylor (D) 43.2%\n|-\n| [[Virginia's 56th House of Delegates district|56th]]\n| [